"2050500217" and "Rev:1.0" is silkscreened on the board in the FCC photos.
The same text is found on: *[[Planet WNRT-617 v2]] *[[Rosewill RNX-N150RT v2]] *[[SMC SMCWBR14S-N5 rev A2]]
Default settings (including the SSID) are per the FCC manual.
The power adapter shown in the FCC photos is a '''Vasata''' P090085-2B1 :(100-240VAC, 50/60Hz, 0.3A -> 9VDC, 0.85A).
